<h3>What preferential treatment to Developing/Least Developed (same category in WTO)?</h3>
<ol>
<li>Non-Reciprocity</li>
<li>Easier Market Access</li>
<li>TRIPS Agreement - Cheaper patented medicines</li></ol>
<h3>How Dispute Settlement?</h3>
<p>3 stages</p>
<ol>
<li>Consultation between parties in case</li>
<li>Dispute Panel - decision accepted by default; Consensus needed to reject</li>
<li>Appellate body (min 3 judge needed) - decision accepted by default; Consensus needed to reject</li></ol>
<p><em>(Shows why&nbsp;soft power needed)</em></p>
<h3>Why Appellate body (lack of judge = no appeal heard) not matter much?</h3>
<ul>
<li>Not all cases go to Appeal stage.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Several countries pact not to go to appeal stage and have arbitration mechanism</li></ul>
